name: Dotcom Computers
tag_list: telecom, networking, switches, routers, refurbished-telecome, shoretel, altigen, allworx
overview:
Dotcom Computers is a retailer of refurbished telecom and networking equipment.

Dotcom Computers has sixteen years of industry experience buying and selling used networking equipment. They specialize in brands such as Adtran, Shoretel, Allworx, Altigen, and Cisco.

They will also buy your surplus telephone, telecom and networking equipment. If your company is interested in selling your telephone sets, PBX systems, NIC cards, voicemail systems, routers or VOIP equipment, Dotcom Computers will send your company an appraisal.
